div.p:
Now that your Grace may grow and goe on in grace, and in the sauing knowledge of the Lord Iesus, let mee intreat you at your best leasure, to peruse this poore yet profitable present: the Lord giue you grace to stand fast in the liberty wherewith Christ Iesus made you free;
         Gal. 5.1. and bee not

 intangled againe with the yoke of bondage.
